org.apache.jena.riot

Class RDFParserRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.riot.RDFParserRegistry

  • public class RDFParserRegistry
extends Object
    The registry of languages and parsers. To register a new parser:
    • Register the language with RDFLanguages
    • Register the parser factory with RDFParserRegistry
